  "prompt": "Where can I get home made birthday cakes at Gold Coast?",
  "response": "If you're looking for homemade-style birthday cakes on the Gold Coast, there are several local bakeries, home-based bakers, and specialty cake shops that can whip up delicious creations. Here are some great options:\n\n### 1. **The Cake That Ate Paris**  \n   - Located in Mermaid Beach, this bakery is known for its homemade-style cakes with beautiful designs.  \n   - They offer custom cakes for birthdays and other occasions.  \n\n### 2. **Belle's Kitchen**  \n   - A home-based bakery in Burleigh Heads, Belle's Kitchen specializes in homemade-style cakes, cupcakes, and desserts.  \n   - Perfect for custom birthday cakes with a personal touch.  \n\n### 3. **Flour & Chocolate**  \n   - Based in Mermaid Waters, this bakery focuses on high-quality, artisan cakes and desserts.  \n   - They can create custom birthday cakes to suit your preferences.  \n\n### 4. **Cake That**  \n   - A boutique cake shop in Southport offering homemade-style cakes with unique flavors.  \n   - Ideal for creative and personalized birthday cakes.  \n\n### 5. **Sugarlips Cakes & Bakes**  \n   - A home-based bakery in Burleigh Heads, Sugarlips offers custom-made cakes, cupcakes, and desserts.  \n   - Great for personalized birthday cakes with a homemade feel.  \n\n### 6. **The Cake Collective**  \n   - Located in Mermaid Beach, this bakery offers a variety of cakes, including custom birthday cakes with a homemade touch.  \n\n### 7. **Gold Coast Local Markets**  \n   - Check out local markets like the Burleigh Farmers Market or the Palm Beach Farmers Market for homemade cakes sold by local bakers.  \n\n### 8. **Facebook Groups and Marketplace**  \n   - Search for local Gold Coast Facebook groups or Marketplace listings where home bakers advertise their services.  \n\n### Tips for Ordering:  \n- Always check reviews and photos of their previous work.  \n- Place your order well in advance, especially for custom designs.  \n- Discuss dietary requirements (e.g., gluten-free, vegan) if needed.  \n\nEnjoy finding the perfect homemade-style cake for your birthday celebration! \ud83c\udf82",
